WEBVTT

01:19.833 --> 01:22.851
IN SOME REGIONS OF INDONESIA,
THERE ARE STILL PESANTRENS...

01:22.875 --> 01:26.059
...THAT UPHOLD THE VALUES OF ANCESTRAL
TEACHINGS AS A HEREDITARY LEGACY...

01:26.083 --> 01:29.184
...WHERE LEADERSHIP OF THE PESANTREN
IS ENTRUSTED ONLY TO MEN.

01:29.208 --> 01:32.625
HOWEVER, AS TIME CHANGES, WOMEN
ARE NOW MORE TRUSTED TO BECOME LEADERS.

01:37.159 --> 01:38.405
Oh, God!

01:38.430 --> 01:40.828
- <i>Astagfirullah.</i>
- Be patient, honey.

01:40.853 --> 01:43.019
Oh, God!

01:47.698 --> 01:49.445
Yeah.

01:49.582 --> 01:51.066
We almost there.

01:51.304 --> 01:52.304
Be patient.

01:52.840 --> 01:54.400
<i>Astaghfirullah.</i>

01:54.437 --> 01:55.437
Be patient.

01:55.825 --> 01:57.700
Say God's name.

01:58.065 --> 01:59.190
Let me check you first, Ma'am.

01:59.245 --> 02:00.505
<i>Astaghfirullah.</i>

02:04.708 --> 02:06.083
Prepare the operation room.

02:07.250 --> 02:09.666
Sir, your wife has to give birth now.

02:11.491 --> 02:12.984
Isn't it supposed to be in two weeks?

02:14.824 --> 02:16.784
<i>Astagfirullah.</i>

02:20.875 --> 02:22.491
Say God's name. Be patient.

02:22.516 --> 02:24.311
- Is everything ready?
- Ready.

02:25.368 --> 02:26.948
Commence the procedure.

02:27.754 --> 02:29.558
We have to do something.

02:29.583 --> 02:32.958
Doc, isn't there any other way
besides womb removal?

02:33.250 --> 02:35.900
This is the only way
to ensure Mrs. Dania's safety.

02:36.500 --> 02:39.708
The tumor can cause severe
bleeding during childbirth.

02:39.971 --> 02:41.346
This is the letter of declaration.

02:42.666 --> 02:43.666
Please sign this.

02:46.125 --> 02:47.125
<i>Bismillah.</i>

03:31.358 --> 03:33.900
Welcome, Sir.

03:35.074 --> 03:37.942
You can see your daughter now.

03:39.462 --> 03:41.224
- I'll leave you two alone.
- Thank you.

03:41.250 --> 03:42.250
I'll take my leave.

03:45.316 --> 03:46.627
<i>Assalamualaikum.</i>

04:16.500 --> 04:18.916
TWELVE YEARS LATER

04:19.000 --> 04:22.000
I told you, but you didn't listen.

04:23.100 --> 04:26.067
<i>My life has been this</i>
<i>beautiful for 12 years.</i>

04:27.541 --> 04:30.333
<i>I was once afraid to build a family.</i>

04:31.516 --> 04:34.433
<i>But thank God, everything has been fine.</i>

04:34.832 --> 04:36.790
<i>But nothing stays fine forever.</i>

04:46.082 --> 04:48.166
This one is different...

04:48.208 --> 04:54.541
One, two, three!

04:55.907 --> 04:59.324
Hey, Ahmad!

05:03.583 --> 05:04.583
Ahmad!

05:04.666 --> 05:05.666
Come here!

05:05.958 --> 05:07.292
Let's go in! It's gonna start soon!

05:07.317 --> 05:10.025
Come on, honey.
The even will begin. Come.

05:10.958 --> 05:13.416
Come on, kids! Get into the mosque!

05:13.708 --> 05:15.250
The even is about to start.

05:15.333 --> 05:16.333
Come in!

05:16.798 --> 05:20.564
If God's willing, we will use this prize...

05:20.630 --> 05:23.070
...to build the new student dormitory.

05:23.117 --> 05:23.664
You're welcome.

05:23.689 --> 05:26.377
I hope you can memorize
more of the Qur'an.

05:26.708 --> 05:30.083
- Thank...
- God!

05:31.024 --> 05:34.899
This pesantren is a very precious
heritage of your great-grandfather.

05:37.041 --> 05:43.166
He dedicated his life to build this free
pesantren for the underprivileged children.

05:45.624 --> 05:49.333
And now, I entrust this pesantren to you.

05:52.316 --> 05:52.942
Dad...

05:53.974 --> 05:59.182
...I'm not sure if I can continue
this family legacy with integrity.

06:03.324 --> 06:06.324
You have to have an heir.

06:07.333 --> 06:08.275
A male heir.

06:09.583 --> 06:12.708
You know Dania can't
have any more children.

06:15.016 --> 06:17.067
I can't possibly hurt her feelings.

06:18.281 --> 06:20.090
What's impossible in this world, Fais?

06:21.208 --> 06:24.708
Especially when your
destiny aligns with His will.

06:31.208 --> 06:31.942
Dad...

06:32.825 --> 06:34.317
...does it have to be a male heir?

06:35.408 --> 06:37.408
Is a woman not worthy
of being a leader?

06:39.115 --> 06:41.532
If God's willing, I can prepare Arumi...

06:42.296 --> 06:44.354
...to be worthy of being
the leader of this pesantren.

06:44.958 --> 06:47.916
This is not about male or female.

06:48.958 --> 06:52.541
This is about the will of our ancestors.

06:53.708 --> 06:56.083
I'm not forcing you to do this, Son.

06:57.266 --> 07:00.441
But I'm leaving a will for you.

07:01.466 --> 07:03.450
If you don't have a male heir...

07:04.616 --> 07:07.858
...it would be better to
discontinue this pesantren.

07:12.291 --> 07:13.025
Dad...

07:15.583 --> 07:16.583
Enough.

07:41.233 --> 07:43.275
<i>Astaghfirullah.</i>

07:51.291 --> 07:53.500
You don't need to feel too guilty...

07:53.583 --> 07:56.500
...for not being able to give Fais a son.

07:58.375 --> 08:00.458
This is fate.

08:05.916 --> 08:08.916
I understand how you feel.

08:10.250 --> 08:12.666
No woman is willing
to share her husband...

08:13.708 --> 08:15.833
...except for one with a big heart...

08:16.500 --> 08:18.166
...who can accept all of this.

08:19.083 --> 08:21.083
But I can't get involved.

08:22.500 --> 08:25.291
Because this is a hereditary will.

08:33.500 --> 08:34.500
Kahfi.

08:34.958 --> 08:38.125
I hope I can come again next month.

08:38.708 --> 08:42.291
Since your dad isn't here anymore,
I have to earn money.

08:43.041 --> 08:45.583
Here, I brought your favorite food.

08:46.083 --> 08:48.625
Ustad, please take care of Kahfi.

08:49.416 --> 08:52.000
- <i>Assalamualaikum.</i>
- <i>Waalaikumsalam.</i> Take care.

08:52.333 --> 08:55.333
I'm worried about the future
of the students here.

08:57.708 --> 09:00.208
Without this pesantren,
where would they go?

09:01.458 --> 09:03.666
Is this God's test for me...

09:06.000 --> 09:08.375
...to test the greatness of my heart?

09:13.250 --> 09:15.666
Do I have to carry this burden with me?

09:19.458 --> 09:20.625
Go walk around.

09:34.706 --> 09:36.958
- Assalamualaikum.
- Waalaikumsalam.

09:37.000 --> 09:39.791
- Are you done with your praying?
- We are.

09:43.024 --> 09:45.024
Get ready for school, okay?

09:45.208 --> 09:46.208
Okay.

09:46.908 --> 09:48.074
I'll make you tea.

09:48.642 --> 09:50.225
With a little sugar, please.

09:50.250 --> 09:51.458
Okay.

09:58.908 --> 10:02.265
Ita called, asking me to go to
an exhibition at her child's school.

10:02.415 --> 10:03.273
Is it okay if I go?

10:04.875 --> 10:08.291
You always meet Ita
when you have something to share to her.

10:08.375 --> 10:10.166
I'll go after I clean up here.

10:12.666 --> 10:14.875
- Okay.
- Thanks, honey.

10:16.899 --> 10:17.660
Honey.

10:25.783 --> 10:26.991
Are you okay?

10:30.408 --> 10:32.700
Yes, I'm okay.

10:34.983 --> 10:36.400
I'm going to clean up.

10:41.775 --> 10:44.358
Huh? Do you really want to find
another wife for your husband?

10:45.125 --> 10:46.166
Ita...

10:46.250 --> 10:47.250
And Fais agrees?

10:50.174 --> 10:54.924
Sis, I've heard of women who wanted
to find another wife for their husband.

10:55.341 --> 10:58.091
But I never expected to hear it from you.

10:59.666 --> 11:02.666
If your intention is genuine and sincere...

11:03.125 --> 11:05.416
...then you're not human.

11:05.791 --> 11:09.000
You're like an golden-hearted
angel fallen from heaven...

11:09.083 --> 11:11.500
...that will become a role model
for wives all over the world.

11:12.041 --> 11:14.041
"Sharing a husband, sharing blessings."

11:14.333 --> 11:16.875
I thought it only
happens in soap operas.

11:17.583 --> 11:18.958
You're too kind.

11:19.416 --> 11:21.791
I just want the pesantren
to continue operating...

11:21.815 --> 11:24.000
...and for the students
not to lose hope.

11:24.875 --> 11:26.750
You're gonna be a national hero soon.

11:26.891 --> 11:31.058
And ask the Kyai to make
you a biography book.

11:31.141 --> 11:34.641
"Dania Salsabilla,
a strong woman full of sacrifice."

11:34.666 --> 11:35.958
So everyone knows about you.

11:36.625 --> 11:38.000
Ita, I'm serious.

11:38.208 --> 11:40.416
And you think I'm not?

11:40.833 --> 11:42.416
Sis, think about it again.

11:42.500 --> 11:45.416
If Fais marries another woman,
wouldn't your life become more complicated?

11:46.458 --> 11:49.757
I always listen to your
stories and your problems,

11:49.782 --> 11:52.198
and I always try to
help in any way I can.

11:52.666 --> 11:56.666
But for this matter, I give up completely.

11:57.208 --> 11:59.125
- Hi. Ita!
- Hey!

11:59.208 --> 12:00.625
You're here!

12:00.708 --> 12:03.083
- How are you?
- I'm fine, thank God.

12:03.166 --> 12:04.958
Let's get a selfie.

12:04.983 --> 12:06.900
- I'll leave, okay?
- I'll catch up with you.

12:07.357 --> 12:10.066
- Let's do this.
- How fun!

12:10.369 --> 12:12.376
It's been a long time, Ita.

12:12.529 --> 12:14.510
I’m so scared, Ita.

12:47.291 --> 12:48.833
Miss. Oh, God!

12:49.000 --> 12:51.416
- I'm so sorry. It was an accident!
- It's okay.

12:52.083 --> 12:54.583
Here. It's okay.

12:54.660 --> 12:56.577
- Sorry.
- Bella. Dania.

12:57.666 --> 12:58.791
Ita?

12:58.875 --> 13:00.458
You know each other?

13:01.166 --> 13:04.791
I accidentally spilled watercolor on her.

13:04.875 --> 13:06.000
I feel bad.

13:06.083 --> 13:07.958
It's okay, really.

13:08.000 --> 13:10.083
I have a spare hijab in my car.

13:10.108 --> 13:11.339
Let me get it for you, okay?

13:11.458 --> 13:13.875
You don't need to, don't bother.
It's fine, seriously.

13:14.708 --> 13:16.333
We'll become close, seriously.

13:16.416 --> 13:19.416
Remember I told you about Bella?

13:19.750 --> 13:20.958
Here she is.

13:21.458 --> 13:23.958
A successful independent woman.

13:24.000 --> 13:27.875
Not only successful in her career,
she also succeeds in educating her child...

13:27.958 --> 13:29.333
...although she's a single mom.

13:29.474 --> 13:31.849
- Wow!
- It's nothing, really.

13:32.958 --> 13:34.516
But I really feel bad.

13:34.541 --> 13:36.458
- It's fine.
- Let me get it for you.

13:36.541 --> 13:39.194
I'll accompany her to the restroom,
get you cleaned up.

13:39.219 --> 13:39.860
Thank you.

13:39.916 --> 13:42.289
- Thank you, Bella.
- Let's go, it's over there.

13:42.456 --> 13:43.863
- Oh, really?
- Yeah.

13:43.903 --> 13:45.823
I didn't expect it either
when I saw the results.

13:46.375 --> 13:48.083
- Thank you.
- Welcome.

13:48.416 --> 13:50.291
- Thank you Bella.
- Welcome.

13:51.083 --> 13:52.083
By the way...

13:52.666 --> 13:54.916
Ita has always been a good listener.

13:56.024 --> 13:57.232
If we share our feelings...

13:57.291 --> 13:59.791
...her input is always good.

14:00.250 --> 14:01.250
I agree.

14:01.532 --> 14:05.108
Ita is like a mother,
who always gives advice.

14:05.708 --> 14:06.833
Thank you all.

14:06.916 --> 14:09.500
I'm already looking old here, huh?

14:10.208 --> 14:11.416
What if you marry another woman?

14:11.625 --> 14:12.625
Are you crazy?

14:13.041 --> 14:14.750
I didn't even think that far.

14:15.208 --> 14:18.916
I have only one goal, which is
how to keep the pesantren going...

14:19.000 --> 14:20.661
...in accordance
with the will that was...

14:20.685 --> 14:22.625
...established since this pesantren
was founded.

14:22.708 --> 14:24.000
That's all!

14:24.083 --> 14:25.666
Such a crazy idea.

14:25.750 --> 14:27.875
I'm only kidding.

14:29.374 --> 14:31.166
- I was just thinking on my feet.
- Thank you.

14:32.166 --> 14:35.583
While Kyai is still healthy,
and you're still healthy too.

14:36.108 --> 14:37.317
We never know how much time we have.

14:37.916 --> 14:41.400
Nurturing a successor takes a long time.

14:42.250 --> 14:44.625
Who knows, maybe you'd
like to open another branch.

14:48.908 --> 14:50.616
You're thinking about it, aren't you?

14:52.666 --> 14:54.266
You're thinking about it!

14:54.291 --> 14:55.666
You're going to marry another woman!

14:55.750 --> 14:57.375
You hit the jackpot!

14:58.291 --> 14:59.089
You're so messed up!

14:59.916 --> 15:01.333
I'm already jealous of you.

15:02.691 --> 15:04.233
No one wants me!

15:15.533 --> 15:17.867
<i>- Assalamualaikum.</i>
<i>- Waalaikumsalam.</i>

15:21.166 --> 15:23.208
Why do you look so fierce?

15:23.458 --> 15:24.108
Why are you late?

15:24.833 --> 15:26.250
You're usually chill.

15:27.283 --> 15:28.949
Why are you late?

15:33.250 --> 15:36.775
You know, I work at KUA.

15:37.958 --> 15:39.750
People got married there.

15:42.000 --> 15:43.333
People got divorced there.

15:44.041 --> 15:45.041
So?

15:47.458 --> 15:50.375
Fais came. He stayed a bit long.

15:50.408 --> 15:52.575
- Oh, God!
- Fais came to KUA?

15:52.916 --> 15:54.083
What was he doing there?

15:54.750 --> 15:57.125
Don't get too close to him,
or else you'll pick up his behavior.

15:57.150 --> 15:58.850
- What behavior?
- Marrying another woman!

15:58.875 --> 16:00.291
Marrying another woman?

16:00.541 --> 16:02.000
Everyone's doing it these days!

16:02.291 --> 16:03.500
If you try doing that...

16:07.041 --> 16:08.708
- Here it is.
- Thank you.

16:09.083 --> 16:10.308
- Here's your table.
- Thank you.

16:10.333 --> 16:11.333
You're welcome.

16:12.750 --> 16:14.833
- Hi!
- Hi!

16:16.166 --> 16:17.375
Ita's not here yet?

16:17.799 --> 16:20.257
She told me she's not coming.

16:20.291 --> 16:22.725
- Why?
- She has diarrhea from food poisoning.

16:22.750 --> 16:24.166
That poor woman.

16:24.250 --> 16:25.541
So, how's it going?

16:25.791 --> 16:27.583
Have you watched all those K-drama?

16:28.291 --> 16:29.791
I have.

16:31.099 --> 16:33.067
The storyline is more or
less the same as my life story.

16:33.333 --> 16:35.791
The difference is I'm
the male character there.

16:39.208 --> 16:41.791
Sorry, Bel. Your husband...

16:42.150 --> 16:43.733
My ex-husband.

16:45.250 --> 16:47.208
I got divorced three years ago.

16:49.875 --> 16:52.375
He left me with tons of problems.

16:56.266 --> 16:59.058
Including the divorce process
that I had to handle on my own.

17:04.008 --> 17:09.133
And I try to raise Ahmad
to the best of my ability.

17:11.407 --> 17:16.075
I don't want Ahmad to think
that he was born into a failed family.

17:22.708 --> 17:24.125
But thankfully...

17:26.416 --> 17:28.583
...my parents always support me.

17:38.625 --> 17:39.625
Just a minute.

17:41.833 --> 17:43.041
How about this, Bobby?

17:43.333 --> 17:45.083
You take care of everything.

17:45.166 --> 17:47.541
If anything happens,
I'll contact you again.

17:47.625 --> 17:48.275
Okay?

17:50.708 --> 17:52.250
- Just go ahead.
- Okay.

17:53.166 --> 17:54.666
Hey, Bella!

17:57.058 --> 18:00.058
I didn't expect to see you here.

18:02.833 --> 18:04.025
What's the matter with you?

18:05.249 --> 18:07.579
You ignore my messages and my calls.

18:08.749 --> 18:09.687
Are you busy?

18:13.166 --> 18:14.004
Bella, listen.

18:15.623 --> 18:20.165
Actually, I've prepared
a good project for you.

18:21.166 --> 18:22.666
It's good for your business.

18:23.666 --> 18:27.791
But if you act like this,
it's hard to make a deal.

18:30.416 --> 18:31.416
Or...

18:34.041 --> 18:36.458
...you want to meet
somewhere more private?

18:38.791 --> 18:41.000
To make the deal easier.
How about that?

18:44.673 --> 18:45.881
You took forever!

18:46.649 --> 18:47.649
- What are you doing?
- Hey!

18:47.875 --> 18:50.375
Stop bothering Bella,
or else I'll report you to the police!

18:51.625 --> 18:53.458
Leave.

18:55.083 --> 18:56.291
Hurry up and leave!

18:56.375 --> 18:57.375
Okay.

18:57.583 --> 18:59.583
- Leave, now!
- Okay. I'll leave now.

19:01.791 --> 19:02.791
Calm down, Dania.

19:06.875 --> 19:07.875
Thank you.

19:08.100 --> 19:12.516
It's okay. I'm used to guys like that.

19:12.583 --> 19:14.833
You can't keep accepting that.

19:14.858 --> 19:16.067
How long are you going to tolerate that?

19:17.125 --> 19:19.375
You're a beautiful single woman.

19:19.458 --> 19:21.416
The slander will be
getting worse every day.

19:28.833 --> 19:30.458
You can do it!

19:30.541 --> 19:31.708
He's good!

19:32.333 --> 19:34.250
Him again, right?

19:35.208 --> 19:37.791
- Hello?
- It's so fun here.

19:37.875 --> 19:40.958
Thank you for taking me
to your family's pesantren.

19:41.041 --> 19:42.333
You're welcome.

19:42.583 --> 19:45.541
I'm the one who should be thankful
that you two can come here.

19:45.625 --> 19:46.750
Oh, God.

19:48.375 --> 19:49.375
Hey, Dania.

19:50.416 --> 19:51.666
Which one is your husband?

19:52.166 --> 19:53.958
He is dealing with something
at the foundation office.

19:54.041 --> 19:55.291
- I'll introduce you to him.
- Shoot!

19:55.375 --> 19:57.166
- He's busy.
- Is that so?

19:59.125 --> 20:00.125
Put it there.

20:01.416 --> 20:03.000
Rock-paper-scissors.

20:06.083 --> 20:07.083
Come on.

20:07.250 --> 20:08.375
Rock-paper-scissors.

20:09.308 --> 20:11.183
Where's Attar's dad?

20:11.208 --> 20:13.541
And where's Ahmad?

20:13.641 --> 20:16.266
He always tells me where he's going.

20:16.349 --> 20:18.266
Let me go find him. Okay?

20:18.291 --> 20:19.291
Rock-paper-scissors.

20:19.492 --> 20:20.908
<i>Assalamualaikum.</i>

20:21.000 --> 20:23.583
<i>Waalaikumsalam.</i>
Ustad.

20:28.416 --> 20:30.750
I didn't expect to see you here, Ahmad.

20:30.833 --> 20:32.125
Did you come with your grandparents?

20:32.208 --> 20:34.708
No. I came here with my mother, Uncle.

20:37.333 --> 20:38.333
Ahmad?

20:40.541 --> 20:43.583
Hey. I was looking for you, you know.

20:44.131 --> 20:47.000
Hey, my friends want
to meet you. Let's go.

20:47.041 --> 20:48.833
- Hey, Ma...
- Let's go.

20:48.916 --> 20:50.208
- Excuse us, Sir. Let's go.
- Yeah.

20:56.316 --> 20:59.024
It was tofu yesterday.
It's chicken today.

21:00.000 --> 21:01.000
Ahmad.

21:02.250 --> 21:07.041
As a guy, I hope you'll
grow up to be like me.

21:07.633 --> 21:08.841
To be a pesantren leader.

21:09.058 --> 21:09.625
Would you like that?

21:10.541 --> 21:13.416
- I'd like that.
- Thank God.

21:16.657 --> 21:20.282
I heard about you from Haji Usman, Bella.

21:21.333 --> 21:23.750
Thank God we are
brought together here.

21:24.291 --> 21:25.291
Thank God.

21:28.625 --> 21:30.166
You know each other, Dania?

21:30.708 --> 21:31.708
Yes, Father.

21:32.399 --> 21:35.524
They're close, like sisters.

21:37.750 --> 21:40.000
But we rarely get to
eat together like this.

21:40.083 --> 21:42.958
- Double date.
- Why double date?

21:43.057 --> 21:46.474
Let's pray that Bella will
get a pious partner soon.

21:46.875 --> 21:48.375
To be Ahmad's new dad.

21:48.682 --> 21:50.349
Amen.

21:50.423 --> 21:53.798
- <i>Assalamualaikum.</i>
- <i>Waalaikumsalam</i>! Here he is!

21:58.875 --> 22:02.791
Here's the guy we've been waiting for.
The pesantren owner.

22:03.208 --> 22:04.416
Dad, come here.

22:07.257 --> 22:08.549
Sorry for being late.

22:08.916 --> 22:11.416
I had a meeting with the teachers
and pesantren management.

22:13.500 --> 22:16.083
Bella, meet my husband, Fais.

22:16.541 --> 22:19.166
Mom, that's Uncle Fais,
who you met earlier.

22:19.916 --> 22:21.041
Yes, honey.

22:28.333 --> 22:30.625
Bella is a nice woman.

22:32.708 --> 22:35.791
I think Fais should
get to know her better.

22:37.591 --> 22:41.191
Who knows, maybe they're a match.

22:44.375 --> 22:49.375
Sorry, but don't you think
you should reconsider your wish?

22:51.033 --> 22:54.616
I'm afraid it will ruin the
happiness of their family.

22:55.891 --> 22:57.432
Especially Dania's.

22:58.424 --> 23:00.216
I stand by my decision.

23:02.682 --> 23:08.224
Sorry, but if we were
blessed with a daughter...

23:08.958 --> 23:10.958
...would you look for another wife?

23:13.590 --> 23:15.066
"If."

23:17.899 --> 23:21.692
When the word is used for something
that's already in the past...

23:23.641 --> 23:25.558
...God doesn't like this word.

23:28.666 --> 23:32.291
I understand what's in your heart.

23:34.449 --> 23:37.858
If this happened...

23:38.916 --> 23:44.483
...and I had to find another
wife for this pesantren...

23:46.641 --> 23:48.557
...what would you do?

23:55.125 --> 23:56.125
Honey.

23:57.916 --> 23:59.541
Honey, wake up.

24:00.750 --> 24:02.166
I want to ask you something.

24:02.833 --> 24:04.541
What, honey?

24:04.916 --> 24:05.858
Oh, dear.

24:07.583 --> 24:11.208
Did you really not get a
head start in meeting Bella?

24:12.932 --> 24:15.192
I told you.

24:16.267 --> 24:18.600
We agreed to not lying to each other.

24:18.625 --> 24:19.833
We have to trust one another.

24:19.916 --> 24:21.333
I trust you.

24:24.458 --> 24:25.458
Do you think she's pretty?

24:27.475 --> 24:29.350
I'm lying if I say she's not.

24:29.375 --> 24:30.958
Everyone would say she is.

24:33.132 --> 24:35.025
But you're still prettier to me.

24:37.767 --> 24:40.567
And did your heart pound
when you first saw her?

24:40.916 --> 24:43.916
Stop this. It's late.

24:44.392 --> 24:47.100
I'm tired. I had to take care
of the pesantren, my work.

24:47.125 --> 24:49.750
And you're asking these
question here at home.

24:50.466 --> 24:52.466
Okay, then. One more question.

24:53.133 --> 24:54.508
Can I ask it before we go to sleep?

24:59.916 --> 25:00.916
Honey...

25:04.474 --> 25:05.849
Would you be...

25:08.991 --> 25:10.699
...Ahmad's father?

25:13.991 --> 25:14.737
Honey?

25:32.375 --> 25:38.500
The details of expenses and
income will be shown here.

25:38.541 --> 25:41.166
Is there anything
you'd like to ask? Sir?

25:41.541 --> 25:44.541
I think it's enough. It's
very detailed already.

25:45.916 --> 25:49.666
O God, I still don't have the knowledge.

25:50.491 --> 25:52.658
Please give me your guidance, God.

25:53.208 --> 25:56.333
May my destiny align with Your will.

25:57.000 --> 25:59.458
One, two, three.

26:00.041 --> 26:01.041
Okay.

26:01.876 --> 26:04.226
- Okay.
- Thanks.

26:13.866 --> 26:18.324
<i>- Assalamualaikum.</i>
<i>- Waalaikumsalam.</i>

26:18.958 --> 26:19.958
Thanks.

26:21.625 --> 26:23.166
Were you at Bella's office?

26:24.750 --> 26:25.916
Why didn't you tell me?

26:27.582 --> 26:31.457
Dad wanted me to accompany him,
it's to tidy up the pesantren's financial.

26:32.333 --> 26:35.291
Bella gave us a lot of advice.
She had good ideas.

26:36.333 --> 26:40.442
One of them is to redesign the pesantren's
social media to make it more modern.

26:41.166 --> 26:42.750
Thank God. Good, then.

26:46.583 --> 26:47.583
Thanks.

26:48.750 --> 26:49.750
In God's name.

26:52.958 --> 26:54.749
Thank God.

26:55.250 --> 26:56.250
Honey.

26:57.666 --> 27:00.291
I've noticed you've been zoning
out a lot lately. What's going on?

27:04.933 --> 27:06.624
Nothing's going on.

27:06.791 --> 27:10.499
Honey, we've been married for years.

27:10.991 --> 27:13.108
I know when you have a problem.

27:19.000 --> 27:20.416
Is it about the pesantren?

27:23.458 --> 27:26.666
Do you want to talk to me about it?
Maybe I can help you find a solution.

27:41.875 --> 27:42.875
Actually...

27:47.891 --> 27:52.432
You know Dad worries too much
about the future of the pesantren.

27:54.416 --> 27:55.791
But I took care of it.

27:56.458 --> 27:57.458
You don't need to worry.

27:59.524 --> 28:00.524
Are you sure?

28:11.750 --> 28:12.750
Honey...

28:14.516 --> 28:15.891
I know everything.

28:18.675 --> 28:22.675
I know you often pray at night.

28:24.574 --> 28:26.866
And I know what you're praying for.

28:31.675 --> 28:33.610
Honey, what are you saying?

28:33.750 --> 28:37.608
Honey! Stop pretending!

28:37.875 --> 28:39.875
It's all about a male heir, isn't it?

28:40.833 --> 28:44.083
Your dad wants you to
have a male successor.

28:44.225 --> 28:47.150
A boy. But I can't give you that!

28:47.375 --> 28:48.375
Honey!

28:48.875 --> 28:50.875
This isn't about a
successor or the pesantren.

28:51.333 --> 28:55.208
And it never occurred to me that I
might make you feel worthless like this.

28:56.516 --> 29:00.025
- Calm down.
- I'm calm!

29:00.541 --> 29:03.083
I've been calm.

29:04.208 --> 29:07.208
Since Arumi was born,
everything changed.

29:08.583 --> 29:12.358
I know you want to have a son.

29:14.016 --> 29:17.266
I know I'm your wife!

29:17.291 --> 29:21.041
I'm your wife.
Don't hide anything else from me!

29:21.125 --> 29:23.333
I know everything!

29:27.966 --> 29:29.627
I feel like everything is weird.

29:30.625 --> 29:31.625
I beg you.

29:34.541 --> 29:36.083
I'm willing to accept it.

29:37.441 --> 29:39.192
I'm willing to accept it, honey.

29:44.375 --> 29:45.750
For you...

29:46.708 --> 29:48.125
For the pesantren...

29:50.083 --> 29:53.083
...I'm willing to sacrifice my feelings.

29:56.500 --> 29:59.375
If you want to have a son...

30:00.075 --> 30:03.491
...allow me to find the
right woman for you.

31:12.916 --> 31:14.499
Go for it, Fais!

31:15.041 --> 31:16.458
Is that how we're doing it now?

31:16.732 --> 31:17.553
Gosh.

31:18.433 --> 31:19.475
In our religion...

31:19.500 --> 31:21.510
...a man doesn't have
to ask for his wife's...

31:21.534 --> 31:23.500
...permission if he wants
to marry another woman.

31:24.774 --> 31:26.482
It's not about permission.

31:27.999 --> 31:31.150
It's about how to be fair
and not to hurt women's feelings.

31:32.000 --> 31:33.916
I know marrying another
woman isn't forbidden.

31:34.500 --> 31:36.000
But it comes with a big responsibility.

31:36.333 --> 31:38.942
Fais, you are able.

31:39.958 --> 31:42.333
You can learn about being fair later.

31:49.250 --> 31:50.250
Sir.

31:50.541 --> 31:52.708
Are you sure Ita can't hear us?

31:54.365 --> 31:58.740
On a day off like today, she likes to
cook while listening to the music. See?

32:00.125 --> 32:01.833
Her headphones look
like a pair of steamed buns.

32:03.416 --> 32:05.541
She'll be like this until
later this afternoon. All good.

32:07.141 --> 32:11.234
For me, I know I'm not capable yet.

32:12.199 --> 32:15.699
My one and only wife there,
she's like the people on the internet.

32:16.250 --> 32:17.458
Angry all the time.

32:18.267 --> 32:20.350
What if she asks you to
marry another woman?

32:20.375 --> 32:21.541
I'll do it!

32:22.041 --> 32:23.416
<i>I'll do it immediately.</i>

32:24.683 --> 32:27.683
Even if she's not fully willing,
I'm still going for it.

32:27.708 --> 32:29.166
I can't hold it any longer.

32:31.208 --> 32:32.500
I'll cut you to pieces!

32:33.416 --> 32:35.333
The eggplant.
She's cutting the eggplant.

32:36.707 --> 32:38.916
You know I'm working at KUA.

32:39.458 --> 32:41.250
I conduct wedding for people every day.

32:41.550 --> 32:43.758
I imagine how their first night
as husbands and wives would be.

32:44.458 --> 32:46.041
I want that too.

32:46.125 --> 32:48.333
Spicy!

32:48.541 --> 32:51.833
Besides, getting married
again isn't a problem.

32:51.916 --> 32:53.041
<i>It's a solution.</i>

32:53.500 --> 32:54.708
It's better than cheating.

32:54.791 --> 32:58.208
It's only an excuse for people
who can't control their lust like you.

32:58.715 --> 33:01.257
Why won't you trust me?

33:02.333 --> 33:04.708
Talk to Ita, then.

33:05.500 --> 33:10.666
No chance!
Even talking to you makes her suspicious.

33:11.025 --> 33:12.816
She looks for me everywhere.

33:13.574 --> 33:14.991
I can't do it.

33:27.916 --> 33:28.916
Sir.

33:29.932 --> 33:31.516
Is that camera on?

33:32.875 --> 33:33.692
It is.

33:34.041 --> 33:35.750
- Does it have audio recording?
- Of course!

33:35.941 --> 33:37.816
- She can hear you, then.
- Of course!

33:38.041 --> 33:40.250
- Wait, what?
- Of course I can hear you.

33:41.625 --> 33:45.166
I've been curious what
you men are talking about.

33:46.125 --> 33:51.333
I just found out
that someone wants to do it, huh?

33:51.649 --> 33:53.065
Take care of my family, okay?

33:53.333 --> 33:56.125
Where are you going?
Hey! I'm not done with the eggplant here.

33:57.291 --> 34:00.250
- This is my office, Dania.
- Praise God!

34:00.366 --> 34:03.283
Your achievement is the dream
of a lot of women, including me.

34:05.599 --> 34:08.933
Single parent, independent, and amazing.

34:09.083 --> 34:11.583
All of this is extraordinary.

34:12.766 --> 34:14.266
It's nothing.

34:14.375 --> 34:15.375
Have a drink.

34:15.708 --> 34:16.708
Thank you.

34:17.458 --> 34:18.583
What do you want to talk about?

34:21.208 --> 34:23.000
I told you once...

34:25.224 --> 34:28.724
...that my womb had to be removed
after giving birth to Arumi.

34:32.541 --> 34:33.708
That means...

34:35.000 --> 34:38.000
...I can't give Fais another heir.

34:40.658 --> 34:45.942
As long as your husband doesn't mind,
you have nothing to worry about.

34:47.250 --> 34:49.250
That's why I came here.

34:50.291 --> 34:51.875
I would like to ask you a favor.

34:54.716 --> 34:58.026
I need your help, to be exact.

35:00.716 --> 35:02.841
Because I think
you're the right woman.

35:08.250 --> 35:09.250
What do you mean?

35:22.807 --> 35:23.470
Bella...

35:27.708 --> 35:31.250
...would you be okay with
Fais being Ahmad's father?

35:40.257 --> 35:43.466
Do you think it will be easy for me
to accept another woman?

35:44.415 --> 35:47.441
I was only trying to help you.
Bella is the right woman.

36:00.883 --> 36:01.615
Honey...

36:05.875 --> 36:08.666
You know it never occurred to me
to marry another woman.

36:12.749 --> 36:15.517
How could you think
that this is the right decision...

36:16.957 --> 36:19.337
...without discussing it with me?

36:19.666 --> 36:22.666
Honey, I've sacrificed everything.

36:23.833 --> 36:25.458
For you. For us.

36:26.299 --> 36:27.924
For the pesantren. For Bella.

36:28.208 --> 36:29.208
Everything!

36:32.750 --> 36:34.484
Do you think it doesn't hurt me?

36:37.666 --> 36:39.083
I'm hurt.

36:54.041 --> 36:54.817
Dania...

36:59.924 --> 37:02.132
I appreciate your decision.

37:05.024 --> 37:06.359
But I can't.

37:10.582 --> 37:12.999
I can't hurt your feelings.

37:13.458 --> 37:14.358
Honey...

37:15.125 --> 37:17.125
...don't say that, please.

37:23.458 --> 37:27.625
This doesn't mean you
have to forget about me.

37:30.041 --> 37:32.333
Bella and I share the same feeling...

37:32.958 --> 37:34.500
...we both can't accept it.

37:37.082 --> 37:40.666
But there's a greater good beyond this.

37:43.533 --> 37:45.775
This is not about having a son.

37:50.500 --> 37:52.083
Or about the pesantren.

37:59.166 --> 38:02.166
This is all about the students.

38:05.333 --> 38:06.708
I know.

38:11.416 --> 38:12.875
But if...

38:14.708 --> 38:19.458
...this is my fate according to God's will,
I accept it.

38:19.708 --> 38:21.708
If God's willing, I accept it.

38:24.541 --> 38:25.958
I can't, Dania.

38:28.149 --> 38:30.149
I can't. I'm not strong enough.

38:43.458 --> 38:44.958
It's your decision.

38:49.825 --> 38:52.450
If you want to find another woman...

38:56.625 --> 38:59.166
...someone better than Bella,
you can do it.

39:05.008 --> 39:06.675
But one thing is important...

39:09.666 --> 39:11.500
...I will never accept it.

39:18.091 --> 39:19.507
I will only accept...

39:24.674 --> 39:27.174
...if it's a woman of my choosing.

39:55.569 --> 39:57.750
FATHER

39:59.333 --> 40:04.125
I'm comfortable living only with Ahmad
without another man in my life.

40:04.591 --> 40:08.591
If God's willing,
Fais can treat you well.

40:09.416 --> 40:13.541
You need a companion
and a good father figure for Ahmad.

40:14.583 --> 40:18.708
There are lots of better women than me
who are more suitable for Fais.

40:19.099 --> 40:22.099
He needs a strong woman,
and that woman is you.

40:22.482 --> 40:23.482
Why me?

40:28.875 --> 40:30.416
I know how you feel.

40:33.708 --> 40:37.541
But life without an imam
and a companion isn't easy.

40:40.083 --> 40:42.583
If God's willing,
Fais can give you all that.

40:48.958 --> 40:49.958
I don't know, Dania.

40:52.807 --> 40:54.807
Whatever your decision, I'll accept it.

40:56.833 --> 41:00.458
I will accept you as Fais' wife.

41:01.166 --> 41:02.750
<i>No one else.</i>

41:27.541 --> 41:31.458
I entrust everything to You, God.

41:36.500 --> 41:40.666
I know You will give me the best.

41:45.250 --> 41:46.916
O God.

41:51.125 --> 41:53.833
O God, I beg you.

41:56.758 --> 42:01.841
Grant me the ability to keep
being devoted to my husband.

42:07.166 --> 42:08.541
O God.

42:13.458 --> 42:17.041
May my fate align with Your will, God.

42:26.000 --> 42:29.000
This isn't a light issue.

42:29.541 --> 42:32.083
He has to do two things.

42:32.708 --> 42:35.625
First, he must perform <i>istikharah</i>.

42:36.541 --> 42:39.250
Asking for God's guidance.

42:40.166 --> 42:42.541
And <i>istisharah</i> means...

42:42.583 --> 42:49.525
...involving competent parties
to provide input, advice, and perspectives.

42:50.549 --> 42:55.465
Because this isn't only about being fair.

42:56.541 --> 42:57.958
Being able to be fair...

42:59.041 --> 43:02.333
...in providing sustenance,
both material and emotional.

43:03.458 --> 43:04.708
To provide home.

43:05.958 --> 43:07.500
To take them out for a trip.

43:07.958 --> 43:09.500
To take them to go on Umrah together.

43:09.916 --> 43:11.333
Do Haji together.

43:11.625 --> 43:16.041
Or to alternate your time every night.

43:16.199 --> 43:20.366
Many things have been forgotten
by many parties in this matter.

43:21.757 --> 43:24.382
All of this, none other than...

43:25.041 --> 43:29.833
...is about seeking God's approval.

43:50.135 --> 43:51.416
Before I give you my answer...

43:52.958 --> 43:54.666
...I have a question for you.

43:57.291 --> 43:59.416
Is this fair for you, Dania?

44:05.474 --> 44:06.474
Bella...

44:08.549 --> 44:10.340
We are both women.

44:11.816 --> 44:14.691
For me, it would never be fair.

44:17.207 --> 44:19.525
But it's not about being fair.

44:21.124 --> 44:22.916
All of this is about a will.

44:23.857 --> 44:26.066
And if God's willing,
this is for the good of all of us.

44:29.682 --> 44:31.349
I will accept this...

44:33.616 --> 44:37.616
...although I still don't know
if this is the best decision.

44:40.849 --> 44:42.474
But I realize, Dania...

44:44.574 --> 44:47.533
...I'm merely a human
that needs a purpose in life.

44:49.357 --> 44:52.566
A purpose where I
desire worldly happiness...

44:55.283 --> 44:57.658
...and earn my place in heaven.

45:12.990 --> 45:14.115
<i>Assalamualaikum.</i>

45:14.791 --> 45:16.124
<i>Waalaikumsalam.</i>

45:18.958 --> 45:20.900
Are you sure about this?

45:33.774 --> 45:35.107
If God's willing.

45:37.708 --> 45:39.333
What I want...

45:41.433 --> 45:43.183
...and what Bella is looking for...

45:47.998 --> 45:50.707
This is all God's will and destiny.

45:57.933 --> 45:59.558
God's approval...

46:02.425 --> 46:04.133
...lies in the approval of one's parents.

46:08.541 --> 46:09.916
God's anger...

46:11.875 --> 46:13.898
...is also the anger of one's parents.

46:22.241 --> 46:25.116
I will be certain to
be able to do this...

46:27.833 --> 46:31.125
...when I have my parents' blessings.

46:36.749 --> 46:38.374
Your parents too, Dania.

46:42.966 --> 46:44.591
And also your parents, Bella.

46:47.291 --> 46:48.541
And Arumi's blessing.

46:56.224 --> 46:57.089
Fais...

46:58.883 --> 47:01.091
Before you get your blessings...

47:02.282 --> 47:03.657
...there's something I need to ask you.

47:07.891 --> 47:10.307
Are you certain you'll
be able to be fair?

47:14.624 --> 47:17.624
Being fair isn't merely
what is seen, Bella.

47:19.849 --> 47:25.557
It's about how I can care for
and protect your feelings.

47:31.125 --> 47:34.208
I'm merely an ordinary
human with limits.

47:38.308 --> 47:40.016
But I promise...

47:42.166 --> 47:44.541
...I will try my best...

47:46.708 --> 47:49.708
...not to wrong any of you.

47:51.716 --> 47:53.341
We are both women.

47:57.316 --> 47:59.816
We want to be spoiled and loved.

48:02.691 --> 48:04.649
If one day...

48:06.616 --> 48:10.825
...Dania and I need
attention at the same time...

48:14.691 --> 48:16.482
...what would you do?

48:17.308 --> 48:18.517
I beg you, Bella...

48:21.291 --> 48:23.666
...never ask me to choose.

48:26.283 --> 48:29.491
Because being in this position
never crossed my mind.

48:33.125 --> 48:34.125
And to be honest...

48:37.500 --> 48:41.291
...I don't know the best way
to face that situation.

48:43.440 --> 48:45.815
Will I be able to divide my feelings?

48:50.491 --> 48:52.949
My feelings have never
been divided, Bella.

48:54.416 --> 48:55.666
They can only grow.

49:00.250 --> 49:01.541
One thing is for sure...

49:05.066 --> 49:07.275
...you two have to
understand one another.

49:09.824 --> 49:11.116
Both of you have to
be fair to one another.

49:13.250 --> 49:14.625
I only want...

49:17.666 --> 49:22.208
...to see both of you
always feel worthy and loved.

49:25.948 --> 49:28.240
Without either of you feeling neglected.

49:39.791 --> 49:41.416
As God has willed.

49:42.966 --> 49:46.966
I didn't expect you to act this far.

49:52.233 --> 49:53.691
May God approve.

50:01.074 --> 50:05.032
You know why I divorced
Dania's father, don't you?

50:11.416 --> 50:16.708
Because he asked me to allow him
to marry another woman.

50:20.082 --> 50:20.856
And you...

50:21.874 --> 50:25.957
I don't understand why you told
Fais to marry another woman.

50:26.300 --> 50:28.514
Don't you know how it feels like
not to be the only one?

50:29.799 --> 50:31.216
To be neglected.

50:31.915 --> 50:32.915
To be thrown aside.

50:36.924 --> 50:39.549
Men are always
tempted with a new one.

50:42.375 --> 50:46.750
I have failed to keep
your father to stay with us.

50:48.899 --> 50:53.714
And now I see you and let you
have the same fate as me.

50:55.423 --> 50:56.296
Never.

51:00.457 --> 51:03.210
Whatever your reason is,
I will never give my blessing!

51:04.750 --> 51:05.750
Mom!

51:18.699 --> 51:20.533
How do you think
your dad will respond?

51:26.866 --> 51:28.283
I don't understand!

51:29.142 --> 51:31.558
Why are you telling me this now, Bella?

51:31.583 --> 51:34.771
How could you accept this
without discussing it with me first?

51:36.641 --> 51:39.141
I would never agree to you
being someone's second wife!

51:39.248 --> 51:40.457
- Honey...
- Darling, shut up.

51:40.816 --> 51:42.232
Don't get involved in this!

51:42.898 --> 51:47.112
In our family, there will never be a
woman who becomes a second wife.

51:47.599 --> 51:50.308
We're a well-regarded family.

51:50.383 --> 51:55.383
How should I respond when someone
says my only child stole someone's wife?

51:56.975 --> 52:00.133
Mom, you don't need to
care about people's opinion.

52:00.591 --> 52:04.510
What's wrong with being a second wife
if the first wife had already approved?

52:04.875 --> 52:06.375
Dania asked me herself.

52:06.516 --> 52:10.308
Although the first wife said they approve,
it still hurts.

52:10.433 --> 52:12.641
How could she ask you that directly?

52:12.808 --> 52:13.808
Maybe there's something's fishy going on.

52:13.833 --> 52:14.833
- Mom...
- Stop.

52:16.125 --> 52:16.846
Enough.

52:17.682 --> 52:22.098
I will never agree to and give my
blessing for you to become a second wife.

52:22.782 --> 52:27.366
Darling, tell your beloved daughter
not to let her shame this family.

52:28.058 --> 52:32.183
From now on,
stop donating to Kyai Abdullah's pesantren.

52:32.299 --> 52:33.108
I don't like it.

52:53.767 --> 52:56.600
Share it to everyone,
so we can check it together.

52:56.625 --> 52:59.583
But if you have any
questions, you can ask directly.

52:59.625 --> 53:01.638
This is also all complete.

53:01.858 --> 53:04.340
- Later...
- Can I see?

53:04.371 --> 53:05.405
We can see it on the first page.

53:10.125 --> 53:11.916
<i>- Assalamualaikum.</i>
<i>- Waalaikumsalam.</i>

53:15.416 --> 53:16.708
Arumi.

53:17.307 --> 53:19.141
Sorry to keep you waiting.

53:26.185 --> 53:27.525
You can do it!

53:30.993 --> 53:31.726
Arumi.

53:32.465 --> 53:33.465
Give us the ball back, please.

53:37.833 --> 53:38.833
Just a minute, please.

53:40.199 --> 53:43.783
Arumi had been waiting
for you until she went asleep.

53:44.649 --> 53:45.815
Were you waiting for me?

53:47.581 --> 53:48.581
I'm sorry.

53:53.432 --> 53:55.932
Don't forget, tomorrow is our day out.

54:25.374 --> 54:27.916
WE'RE AT THE LOCATION.
WHERE ARE YOU?

54:28.191 --> 54:29.857
Oh, God!

54:48.941 --> 54:49.941
Honey...

54:51.766 --> 54:53.724
- Honey, I...
- My mom is right.

54:56.240 --> 54:59.400
After marrying Bella,
you might leave me.

55:04.607 --> 55:08.567
But if it does happen,
I only have one request.

55:15.433 --> 55:17.433
Don't ever leave Arumi.

55:23.000 --> 55:24.000
Honey...

55:24.666 --> 55:25.874
Honey, wait.

55:26.808 --> 55:29.998
- Honey, I'm trying to explain here.
- You don't need to explain anything to me.

55:30.257 --> 55:33.049
The important thing now is
you tell everything about us to Arumi.

55:57.207 --> 55:58.623
Arumi.

56:05.074 --> 56:06.616
School break is just
around the corner, isn't it?

56:08.532 --> 56:10.324
Where do you want to go for your holiday?
I'll take you.

56:12.149 --> 56:14.941
No need. You're busy.

56:15.815 --> 56:18.565
You don't have time for me anymore.

56:20.648 --> 56:23.732
Why do you say that?

56:29.541 --> 56:30.541
I promise you...

56:31.765 --> 56:33.890
...I will keep you
company during your break.

56:34.458 --> 56:36.250
Okay? Where do you want to go?

56:36.915 --> 56:40.415
There's no need. I prefer
to go to Grandma Hanna.

56:41.116 --> 56:42.532
I miss her.

56:51.158 --> 56:52.574
Actually...

56:56.249 --> 56:59.175
...there's something we need to tell you.

57:05.341 --> 57:06.400
So...

57:13.474 --> 57:14.458
So?

57:18.699 --> 57:19.908
So, what?

57:27.641 --> 57:31.266
If you're not gonna say anything,
let me ask you something.

57:34.983 --> 57:38.609
Why was I born a girl?

57:40.691 --> 57:42.316
Why not a boy?

57:43.625 --> 57:45.542
It would have made both of you happier.

57:46.657 --> 57:47.657
More happiness.

58:03.541 --> 58:04.541
Fais.

58:05.333 --> 58:08.416
There's only one
condition to share your love.

58:09.375 --> 58:12.166
It is to be fair.

58:13.666 --> 58:16.291
And it's not easy.

58:17.782 --> 58:19.698
If you worry...

58:20.749 --> 58:23.041
...that you won't be able to do it,
that's normal.

58:23.716 --> 58:27.841
Because Allah says in the Qur'an...

58:37.774 --> 58:43.316
You will never be able to be
perfectly just between your wives...

58:44.283 --> 58:47.033
...even if you desire to do so.

58:47.958 --> 58:52.375
That's why the intention is very important.

58:53.541 --> 58:56.041
If you do it only for Allah...

58:56.500 --> 58:58.791
...well, do it, then.

58:59.758 --> 59:02.966
But if it is merely a
temptation of desire...

59:04.192 --> 59:07.775
...moreover, Satan's temptation...

59:09.815 --> 59:12.190
...only one wife is enough.

59:14.250 --> 59:15.833
- Got it?
- Yes, Ustad.

59:15.916 --> 59:18.541
<i>- Assalamualaikum.</i>
<i>- Waalaikumsalam.</i>

59:19.833 --> 59:21.458
He's the head of KUA.

59:22.141 --> 59:23.266
He's my teacher too.

59:23.891 --> 59:27.317
That's why his advices
are always on point.

59:27.800 --> 59:28.800
You heard him.

59:29.691 --> 59:31.774
Just marry the other woman.

59:32.290 --> 59:34.067
That's what you keep saying.

59:35.141 --> 59:38.516
Why are you so eager
for me to marry Bella?

59:42.075 --> 59:44.616
Stop accusing me.

59:45.091 --> 59:48.817
My name may be Untung,
but luckily I only have one wife.

59:49.516 --> 59:53.516
Because I know if I have another wife,
my intention might not be true.

59:53.732 --> 59:55.441
But you're different.

00:59:55.857 --> 01:00:00.273
You are asked to save the students
and to save a divorcee.

01:00:02.725 --> 01:00:05.100
And it's your own wife
who asked you that.

01:00:05.607 --> 01:00:07.191
What a nice life you have.

01:00:08.266 --> 01:00:12.557
And looking at the divorcée, if this
is a movie, I'd like to be the stuntman.

01:00:13.041 --> 01:00:14.291
What more do you expect?

01:00:15.599 --> 01:00:18.433
What should I do? I need your help.

01:00:18.458 --> 01:00:19.458
Such a dumb question!

01:00:20.333 --> 01:00:22.541
Didn't I make myself clear?

01:00:23.751 --> 01:00:26.475
By the way, have you done <i>istikharah</i>?

01:00:26.575 --> 01:00:27.866
Ask God.

01:00:29.408 --> 01:00:30.783
After that, ask me again.

01:00:33.624 --> 01:00:34.874
You think too much.

01:00:36.116 --> 01:00:38.324
Blessed with so much,
but still confused.

01:00:38.809 --> 01:00:41.475
Is Ita okay with us talking like this?

01:00:41.558 --> 01:00:43.433
Well... Wait, my wife.

01:00:46.682 --> 01:00:49.641
Right. She can pop up here suddenly!

01:00:54.791 --> 01:00:56.958
Oh my God.

01:00:57.041 --> 01:00:58.041
What?

01:00:58.833 --> 01:01:00.166
Your queen is here.

01:01:00.191 --> 01:01:01.191
Don't look at her!

01:01:02.125 --> 01:01:03.416
Don't look at her.

01:01:03.500 --> 01:01:04.500
Or else she'll come here.

01:01:04.541 --> 01:01:05.466
What should I say?

01:01:05.491 --> 01:01:07.833
Just say that I'm working,
conducting weddings.

01:01:07.900 --> 01:01:10.433
- She's coming.
- Stop looking at her!

01:01:10.750 --> 01:01:12.166
I'm done for here.

01:01:13.199 --> 01:01:15.199
Fais, where's Untung?

01:01:16.125 --> 01:01:17.125
Don't tell her.

01:01:17.516 --> 01:01:19.308
Don't say anything.
Pretend that you're a mute.

01:01:25.416 --> 01:01:26.791
Fais, where is she?

01:01:30.524 --> 01:01:33.107
What are you doing there?

01:01:33.850 --> 01:01:34.850
What are you looking for?

01:01:34.899 --> 01:01:35.899
My phone fell.

01:01:37.250 --> 01:01:38.250
What are you doing here?

01:01:38.867 --> 01:01:40.617
Let's go home. Come.

01:01:41.141 --> 01:01:42.141
I'm going home.

01:01:44.083 --> 01:01:45.083
Take care.

01:01:45.640 --> 01:01:46.849
Come on. Okay?

01:01:47.833 --> 01:01:48.833
Fais...

01:01:53.708 --> 01:01:55.000
This is a struggle.

01:01:55.958 --> 01:01:57.083
This is a tough test.

01:01:59.249 --> 01:02:01.249
Everyone must have
the courage to face it.

01:02:03.741 --> 01:02:06.366
All great heroes overcame this.

01:02:11.258 --> 01:02:13.467
It stings!

01:02:18.975 --> 01:02:21.683
How does it feel? It stings?

01:02:21.933 --> 01:02:23.858
I told you not to get close to him.

01:02:24.149 --> 01:02:26.316
But you still do it discreetly.

01:02:26.600 --> 01:02:26.935
Yes.

01:02:26.960 --> 01:02:28.975
I want you to know how
it feels like for women.

01:02:29.059 --> 01:02:29.318
Yes.

01:02:29.343 --> 01:02:30.651
To have another person
in your relationship...

01:02:30.743 --> 01:02:31.616
It hurts.

01:02:31.743 --> 01:02:33.703
- Yes.
- Here. Some more for you.

01:02:35.716 --> 01:02:36.716
Some more!

01:02:37.724 --> 01:02:39.183
Not strong enough.

01:02:39.208 --> 01:02:42.083
I can't. What if you fall?

01:02:42.458 --> 01:02:44.250
You never fail.

01:02:48.015 --> 01:02:51.807
You've raised me to
be a strong woman.

01:02:53.874 --> 01:02:55.291
Just like you.

01:02:56.125 --> 01:02:57.791
<i>- Again!</i>
<i>- Again!</i>

01:03:02.091 --> 01:03:03.675
Does your heart not hurt?

01:03:09.508 --> 01:03:10.967
It hurts, Mom.

01:03:14.865 --> 01:03:17.449
It really hurts.

01:03:21.275 --> 01:03:24.608
But I'm trying to accept it for God.

01:03:27.865 --> 01:03:32.441
And I'm trying to be
grateful for this ache.

01:03:34.632 --> 01:03:38.549
Mom, this may be God's test.

01:03:42.958 --> 01:03:49.375
Maybe God wants to know how big my
love for Him is compared to other things.

01:03:59.324 --> 01:04:03.324
I'm begging for your blessing, Mom...

01:04:05.750 --> 01:04:08.916
...so God will approve of this journey.

01:04:11.875 --> 01:04:16.875
And so God gives me strength
to get through all this.

01:04:19.641 --> 01:04:23.766
I'm begging for your blessing.
I'm begging you.

01:04:33.558 --> 01:04:36.192
Arumi. Which one do you like?

01:04:41.849 --> 01:04:42.849
Your dad...

01:04:44.515 --> 01:04:46.099
...has a beautiful flower.

01:04:47.291 --> 01:04:48.291
Your mother.

01:04:49.415 --> 01:04:54.231
Soon, he will add another flower.

01:04:55.874 --> 01:04:57.416
A new mother...

01:04:58.533 --> 01:05:00.116
...in your life.

01:05:06.499 --> 01:05:07.582
Two flowers...

01:05:09.849 --> 01:05:14.275
...will make your
garden more beautiful.

01:05:17.958 --> 01:05:19.750
So, I will have two mothers?

01:05:21.032 --> 01:05:22.032
Yes, Arumi.

01:05:27.766 --> 01:05:29.474
Arumi, Mom.

01:05:30.500 --> 01:05:33.083
You look like you're having so
much fun with your Grandma.

01:05:33.600 --> 01:05:35.641
It looks like you've forgotten us.

01:05:36.967 --> 01:05:40.258
Dad, am I gonna have a new mother?

01:05:49.707 --> 01:05:50.791
You do know...

01:05:52.324 --> 01:05:57.810
...that your Mom and I
love you so much, don't you?

01:06:05.183 --> 01:06:06.892
You know Auntie Bella?

01:06:12.132 --> 01:06:13.132
So...

01:06:16.583 --> 01:06:17.958
...your mom and I...

01:06:20.199 --> 01:06:22.615
...want her to be a new
member of our family.

01:06:25.591 --> 01:06:27.966
So, you're going to get a new mother.

01:06:31.141 --> 01:06:33.046
You're going to have two mothers...

01:06:35.575 --> 01:06:38.158
...who will love you.

01:06:40.841 --> 01:06:42.633
But why two?

01:06:44.048 --> 01:06:45.673
I have one already.

01:06:54.949 --> 01:06:56.366
You must be confused.

01:06:58.541 --> 01:07:01.916
But your dad and I
have talked about it.

01:07:03.958 --> 01:07:08.500
If God's willing, Auntie Bella
will be able to give you happiness...

01:07:09.750 --> 01:07:11.541
...and take care of you too.

01:07:15.291 --> 01:07:21.208
But Arumi's scared she won't love
Auntie Bella like she loves Mommy.

01:07:22.199 --> 01:07:23.199
It's okay.

01:07:27.083 --> 01:07:31.500
The love will grow as time goes by.

01:07:34.583 --> 01:07:37.875
You can get to know her slowly.

01:07:48.420 --> 01:07:49.220
Wait.

01:07:53.098 --> 01:07:54.098
<i>Assalamualaikum.</i>

01:07:55.958 --> 01:07:58.541
- It hurts!
- Be patient.

01:07:58.833 --> 01:08:00.708
- It hurts, Mom!
- <i>Assalamualaikum.</i>

01:08:00.799 --> 01:08:01.799
Bella?

01:08:02.766 --> 01:08:04.641
- <i>Waalaikumsalam.</i>
- What's wrong with Ahmad?

01:08:04.666 --> 01:08:07.500
I don't know. When I got home,
he was in pain already.

01:08:07.861 --> 01:08:09.541
- Let's take him to the doctor.
- Yeah.

01:08:10.215 --> 01:08:13.215
- Let's go to the doctor.
- Come on. Be careful.

01:08:14.791 --> 01:08:16.916
Let's go to the doctor, Ahmad.

01:08:17.282 --> 01:08:18.657
- Be careful.
- Okay.

01:08:21.942 --> 01:08:24.567
Thank you for taking
Ahmad to the hospital.

01:08:27.124 --> 01:08:29.916
I don't know how it
would be without you.

01:08:33.524 --> 01:08:36.232
Everything is by God's permission.

01:08:36.582 --> 01:08:38.128
- <i>Assalamualaikum</i> Ahmad?
- <i>Assalamualaikum.</i>

01:08:38.153 --> 01:08:39.695
- <i>Waalaikumsalam.</i>
- <i>Waalaikumsalam.</i>

01:08:40.391 --> 01:08:41.125
Ahmad?

01:08:41.150 --> 01:08:41.715
Ma'am.

01:08:41.765 --> 01:08:42.432
Mom.

01:08:43.000 --> 01:08:44.416
Why is he here?

01:08:50.215 --> 01:08:52.590
Darling, what's wrong?

01:09:12.049 --> 01:09:13.840
You should've told us, Bella...

01:09:17.466 --> 01:09:19.817
...that your mother
didn't give her blessing.

01:09:26.324 --> 01:09:27.840
I didn't know what to say.

01:09:35.482 --> 01:09:37.052
If God's willing, there will be a solution.

01:09:38.624 --> 01:09:41.483
For now, let's just
focus on Ahmad's health.

01:09:58.183 --> 01:10:00.192
Honey, I'm leaving now, okay?

01:10:00.914 --> 01:10:02.456
I have an impromptu meeting.

01:10:03.934 --> 01:10:04.847
<i>Bismillah.</i>

01:10:08.816 --> 01:10:10.441
Pick up Arumi later, okay?

01:10:11.091 --> 01:10:12.674
- I'm afraid I won't make it.
- <i>Bye. Assalamualaikum.</i>

01:10:13.008 --> 01:10:14.966
Yes. <i>Waalaikumsalam.</i>

01:10:15.699 --> 01:10:19.782
Bella just called to ask us to accompany
Ahmad at the hospital for a short time.

01:10:19.849 --> 01:10:21.808
Because she can't reschedule her meeting.

01:10:21.974 --> 01:10:22.974
Now?

01:10:27.250 --> 01:10:29.708
His grandma is still there, right?
Won't that be a problem?

01:10:30.365 --> 01:10:31.782
She went home already.

01:10:32.108 --> 01:10:33.608
This won't take long.

01:10:36.266 --> 01:10:38.016
Okay, I'll get my bag.

01:10:44.183 --> 01:10:46.641
Thank God he's in good condition.

01:10:46.666 --> 01:10:48.416
If God's willing, Ahmad
can go home today.

01:10:48.941 --> 01:10:52.524
That's great. If you keep your spirit up,
your recovery will be quick.

01:10:53.432 --> 01:10:58.307
If Father didn't leave,
he'd be here to accompany me.

01:11:02.882 --> 01:11:05.299
Sir, Ma'am, I'll leave.

01:11:05.642 --> 01:11:07.475
- Thank you. <i>Assalamualaikum.</i>
- <i>Waalaikumsalam.</i>

01:11:07.500 --> 01:11:08.500
Thank you so much, Doc.

01:11:23.916 --> 01:11:26.333
So, the total expense...

01:11:27.208 --> 01:11:29.083
- ...is this much.
- Okay.

01:11:31.416 --> 01:11:33.208
Excuse me, Ma'am. You
have an incoming call.

01:11:38.316 --> 01:11:39.217
Yes, Dania?

01:11:39.291 --> 01:11:41.958
<i>Bella, come to the hospital now.</i>

01:11:56.583 --> 01:11:57.629
Dania.

01:12:02.000 --> 01:12:02.900
Hi.

01:12:03.807 --> 01:12:04.624
Bella.

01:12:28.000 --> 01:12:28.608
Sir.

01:12:33.299 --> 01:12:34.025
Mr. Ustad.

01:12:36.949 --> 01:12:37.949
Sorry, Mr. Ryan.

01:12:39.525 --> 01:12:41.058
I'm not an Ustad.

01:12:41.132 --> 01:12:42.340
Oh, you're not?

01:12:43.049 --> 01:12:43.900
What, then?

01:12:45.007 --> 01:12:48.132
What are you here for exactly?

01:12:51.775 --> 01:12:52.900
Are you inquiring about my intentions?

01:12:55.799 --> 01:12:57.216
My intention for coming here...

01:12:58.499 --> 01:12:59.582
...is to tell you...

01:13:01.099 --> 01:13:02.599
...to stay away from Bella.

01:13:04.583 --> 01:13:06.000
Bella is mine.

01:13:06.791 --> 01:13:09.708
Don't you dare ruining my family.

01:13:12.058 --> 01:13:13.058
Got it?

01:13:43.990 --> 01:13:46.990
After you left without
any news for this long...

01:13:47.166 --> 01:13:49.707
...now you want to get
back together with me?

01:13:51.458 --> 01:13:53.458
Where have you been all this time?

01:13:53.991 --> 01:13:56.233
I raised Ahmad by myself!

01:13:58.790 --> 01:13:59.790
I know, Bella.

01:14:00.965 --> 01:14:03.174
But it's not without reason.

01:14:05.975 --> 01:14:09.350
I just didn't want to
involve you in my problem.

01:14:13.475 --> 01:14:15.350
Everyone was looking for me.

01:14:18.858 --> 01:14:20.774
But it's all settled now.

01:14:25.257 --> 01:14:26.632
I have repented.

01:14:28.549 --> 01:14:29.549
It's too late, Ryan.

01:14:31.474 --> 01:14:32.474
We're done.

01:14:34.257 --> 01:14:36.424
You can't get back into my life.

01:14:37.333 --> 01:14:38.108
No.

01:14:38.933 --> 01:14:40.058
Nothing is ever late.

01:14:42.133 --> 01:14:43.925
I still care so much about you.

01:14:45.574 --> 01:14:47.699
And I'm sure you still care about me.

01:14:49.675 --> 01:14:50.650
And Ahmad...

01:14:51.649 --> 01:14:53.483
He needs a father figure.

01:15:00.674 --> 01:15:02.049
Give me a chance.

01:15:02.582 --> 01:15:05.541
I promise not to leave you ever again.

01:15:07.375 --> 01:15:08.458
Bella.

01:15:08.607 --> 01:15:09.607
Bella!

01:15:10.491 --> 01:15:13.275
I won't leave until
you give me a chance.

01:15:33.283 --> 01:15:34.825
<i>I have repented.</i>

01:15:36.458 --> 01:15:38.583
<i>I still care so much about you.</i>

01:15:41.241 --> 01:15:42.241
<i>And Ahmad...</i>

01:15:43.257 --> 01:15:45.049
<i>He needs a father figure.</i>

01:15:54.708 --> 01:15:55.610
Yes, Boss.

01:16:01.191 --> 01:16:03.691
<i>No, I've talked to her.</i>

01:16:04.416 --> 01:16:06.791
<i>Yes. No. I will get it this time.</i>

01:16:07.041 --> 01:16:09.250
<i>Just give me time. Just a little time.</i>

01:16:09.958 --> 01:16:13.125
<i>After we reconcile,</i>
<i>I will get the money.</i>

01:16:13.708 --> 01:16:16.124
I will pay off all of my debts. Okay?

01:16:16.433 --> 01:16:18.849
I also need capital.
I want to play again...

01:16:22.083 --> 01:16:23.375
Bella, no. This is...

01:16:23.916 --> 01:16:27.124
No, Bella. This is only a joke. Bella!

01:16:27.833 --> 01:16:28.833
Idiot!

01:16:31.016 --> 01:16:32.808
So, is that the situation?

01:16:34.558 --> 01:16:40.017
Honey, what if Mr. Usman stops
his donation to our pesantren?

01:16:40.883 --> 01:16:41.783
Honey...

01:16:42.757 --> 01:16:46.317
We've faced much harder
challenges than this together.

01:16:47.450 --> 01:16:49.575
Fortune is not in their hands.

01:16:50.516 --> 01:16:51.849
It's in God's hands.

01:16:54.808 --> 01:16:56.141
We're going to come to them.

01:16:57.982 --> 01:16:59.150
Not for the donation.

01:17:01.700 --> 01:17:03.116
But for you, Fais.

01:17:14.500 --> 01:17:15.791
They're going to come here?

01:17:16.166 --> 01:17:17.625
What for?

01:17:18.208 --> 01:17:19.541
To ask for your hand for marriage?

01:17:20.482 --> 01:17:22.607
They know I don't give my blessing.

01:17:22.632 --> 01:17:24.091
They really don't know their place.

01:17:25.091 --> 01:17:28.175
They know I never agree
for my daughter to be a second wife.

01:17:28.699 --> 01:17:29.699
But why are they still so daring?

01:17:31.149 --> 01:17:33.107
I'm speaking not because of my ego.

01:17:36.000 --> 01:17:37.208
You don't know this.

01:17:38.740 --> 01:17:43.233
But it's been hard for me to open my heart
to men because of the trauma Ryan gave me.

01:17:45.315 --> 01:17:46.607
- And this time...
- No!

01:17:47.441 --> 01:17:51.024
Whatever your reason is,
I will never give you my blessing.

01:17:51.998 --> 01:17:54.192
What's so great about Fais?

01:17:55.007 --> 01:17:57.174
He may not be a great person.

01:18:02.283 --> 01:18:03.491
But if God's willing...

01:18:05.141 --> 01:18:08.266
...he's the right person
to guide me to heaven.

01:18:11.991 --> 01:18:13.491
Fais is sincere.

01:18:15.184 --> 01:18:17.725
He's willing to do
anything for me and Ahmad.

01:18:17.775 --> 01:18:19.191
Don't involve Ahmad in this!

01:18:20.408 --> 01:18:24.325
I don't like that you involve
Ahmad to defend Fais. No!

01:18:26.774 --> 01:18:29.566
You always want me to be happy,
but only in your way.

01:18:34.082 --> 01:18:35.207
But please...

01:18:39.883 --> 01:18:42.674
...this time, I want to
be happy in my own way.

01:18:55.833 --> 01:18:59.833
Whatever their purpose is,
as long as it has good intention...

01:19:01.324 --> 01:19:03.856
...we have to welcome any
guests who come our way.

01:19:23.049 --> 01:19:24.049
Fais...

01:19:30.149 --> 01:19:31.149
Wake up.

01:19:32.407 --> 01:19:34.282
Let's do prayer together.

01:20:17.734 --> 01:20:20.581
<i>Assalamualaikum warahmatullah.</i>

01:20:21.454 --> 01:20:23.241
<i>Assalamualaikum warahmatullah.</i>

01:21:48.665 --> 01:21:54.623
We come here not to ask Bella
to be a part of our family...

01:21:56.433 --> 01:21:58.381
...as Fais' companion.

01:22:00.574 --> 01:22:02.115
We're here to apologize...

01:22:03.158 --> 01:22:07.116
...for our actions that may
have hurt you and your family.

01:22:09.332 --> 01:22:13.147
I'm the one who is
responsible for all this.

01:22:14.341 --> 01:22:17.552
I come here this afternoon
on behalf of Fais...

01:22:18.958 --> 01:22:23.808
...to discontinue his pursuit of
making Bella his companion...

01:22:27.282 --> 01:22:29.990
...and to uphold our
relationship as fellow Muslims.

01:22:30.974 --> 01:22:34.766
We meet for the sake of Allah
and we part for the sake of Allah.

01:22:35.441 --> 01:22:37.107
For the future of the pesantren...

01:22:38.140 --> 01:22:40.140
...we will find another solution.

01:22:47.692 --> 01:22:49.108
You don't need to, Kyai.

01:22:51.291 --> 01:22:53.458
The pesantren doesn't
need to find another solution.

01:22:58.299 --> 01:22:59.299
Because I...

01:23:04.250 --> 01:23:05.269
I...

01:23:12.432 --> 01:23:14.807
I give my blessing...

01:23:17.125 --> 01:23:20.542
...for Bella to be Fais' wife.

01:23:30.141 --> 01:23:31.683
You're right, darling.

01:23:34.941 --> 01:23:41.274
I always try to make you
happy, but only in my way.

01:23:42.324 --> 01:23:44.991
Even though it's not necessarily right.

01:23:48.632 --> 01:23:51.632
Now, it's time for you...

01:23:52.866 --> 01:23:55.292
...to find happiness in your own way.

01:23:56.741 --> 01:23:58.741
Because you're the one living it.

01:23:59.983 --> 01:24:03.517
And I'm sure...

01:24:06.041 --> 01:24:07.041
I'm sure...

01:24:08.674 --> 01:24:12.507
...Allah knows what's best for you.

01:24:15.516 --> 01:24:17.891
If God's willing, I...

01:24:21.049 --> 01:24:22.341
...give you my blessing.

01:24:33.023 --> 01:24:35.898
But before you step any further...

01:24:36.808 --> 01:24:37.942
...I have a question.

01:24:40.107 --> 01:24:44.858
Being a second wife isn't easy.

01:24:46.208 --> 01:24:48.000
It's not easy at all.

01:24:49.208 --> 01:24:50.416
Are you ready for that?

01:24:51.875 --> 01:24:54.000
Are you ready, darling?

01:25:02.317 --> 01:25:04.192
I'm not entirely sure.

01:25:07.866 --> 01:25:11.408
But this might be the
answer to my prayers.

01:25:17.333 --> 01:25:23.250
If being a second wife is God's will
to prevent false accusations...

01:25:24.507 --> 01:25:26.507
...and be my path to heaven...

01:25:32.357 --> 01:25:34.317
...if God's willing, I accept it.

01:25:37.291 --> 01:25:38.750
Praise be to God.

01:25:39.916 --> 01:25:40.916
Darling.

01:25:55.691 --> 01:25:58.108
- Bella!
- Oh, God!

01:25:58.457 --> 01:25:59.832
We're not done.

01:26:01.363 --> 01:26:02.809
- Ryan.
- Bella.

01:26:04.808 --> 01:26:05.808
Come here.

01:26:06.516 --> 01:26:08.933
- Hey.
- What are you doing here?

01:26:09.008 --> 01:26:10.008
Leave!

01:26:10.683 --> 01:26:11.683
You're kicking me out?

01:26:12.391 --> 01:26:15.891
Do you forget that I also
have the right to meet Ahmad?

01:26:17.558 --> 01:26:20.683
- I will take Ahmad away from here.
- No, you don't have the right to take him.

01:26:20.708 --> 01:26:21.875
- I have!
- No!

01:26:25.041 --> 01:26:28.359
Okay. If you don't want me
to take Ahmad away...

01:26:29.258 --> 01:26:32.466
...give me back my money.
Give me back all my money!

01:26:32.916 --> 01:26:34.125
I need that money now.

01:26:34.275 --> 01:26:37.567
You've lost all your money for gambling.
Now, leave.

01:26:37.833 --> 01:26:38.833
Leave!

01:26:41.608 --> 01:26:43.774
A real man never hits a woman.

01:26:50.640 --> 01:26:51.640
Mom!

01:26:52.166 --> 01:26:53.666
Ahmad.

01:26:54.291 --> 01:26:56.541
I don't want to have an evil father.

01:27:12.541 --> 01:27:13.541
Fais.

01:27:14.500 --> 01:27:16.083
- Bella.
- Mom.

01:27:17.541 --> 01:27:20.416
I don't want to see you in
front of my family ever again.

01:27:21.073 --> 01:27:22.650
Or else I'll put you in prison.

01:27:33.333 --> 01:27:40.976
<i>And if you fear that you</i>
<i>will not deal justly with the...</i>

01:27:41.000 --> 01:27:48.642
<i>...orphan girls, then marry</i>
<i>those that please you of women,</i>

01:27:48.666 --> 01:27:54.416
<i>two or three or four.</i>

01:27:55.316 --> 01:28:00.307
<i>But if you fear that</i>
<i>you will not be just,</i>

01:28:00.331 --> 01:28:05.482
<i>then one or those your</i>
<i>right hand possesses.</i>

01:28:06.091 --> 01:28:14.049
<i>That is more suitable</i>
<i>that you may not incline.</i>

01:28:15.250 --> 01:28:16.250
Fais?

01:28:17.083 --> 01:28:18.083
Shall we start?

01:28:29.974 --> 01:28:31.682
In the name of God.

01:28:32.232 --> 01:28:36.357
I marry and give you in marriage,
Fais Hanip son of Abdullah...

01:28:36.633 --> 01:28:41.300
...to my daughter,
Bella Anindhiya daughter of Usman...

01:28:41.442 --> 01:28:44.192
...with a dowry of a complete set
of prayer equipment, paid in cash.

01:28:45.708 --> 01:28:47.541
I seek forgiveness from Allah.

01:28:51.666 --> 01:28:52.666
Fais.

01:28:54.791 --> 01:28:55.791
Can you carry on?

01:29:03.849 --> 01:29:04.849
Forgive me, Sir.

01:29:07.132 --> 01:29:07.858
Can you...

01:29:09.199 --> 01:29:11.074
...give me some time?

01:29:31.482 --> 01:29:34.607
It looks like you've fallen
in love with my husband.

01:29:36.766 --> 01:29:39.308
- Forgive me, Dania.
- It's okay.

01:29:44.124 --> 01:29:45.832
You don't need to apologize.

01:29:49.199 --> 01:29:51.199
My heart aches all of a sudden.

01:29:55.874 --> 01:29:58.082
I'm hesitant to continue this.

01:29:59.508 --> 01:30:01.758
Do you want to cancel this wedding?

01:30:13.424 --> 01:30:14.674
Or maybe...

01:30:16.048 --> 01:30:17.923
...we should do <i>istikharah</i> now.

01:30:19.074 --> 01:30:20.865
Let's ask for the best from God.

01:30:23.374 --> 01:30:25.166
Forgive me, Arumi.

01:30:28.675 --> 01:30:30.800
You're going to give
me your blessing, right?

01:30:33.858 --> 01:30:35.483
But you have to promise me...

01:30:37.167 --> 01:30:40.625
...that you'll still love
me and my mother.

01:30:44.250 --> 01:30:45.250
Yes, darling.

01:30:47.399 --> 01:30:48.399
I promise.

01:31:09.815 --> 01:31:12.320
<i>Waalaikumsalam warahmatullahi</i>
<i>wabarakatuh.</i>

01:31:12.358 --> 01:31:15.893
<i>Waalaikumsalam warahmatullahi</i>
<i>wabarakatuh.</i>

01:31:26.666 --> 01:31:27.958
Forgive me.

01:31:36.707 --> 01:31:40.332
I heard all about it from Dania.

01:31:46.150 --> 01:31:47.150
Fais...

01:31:50.416 --> 01:31:51.416
Today...

01:31:55.099 --> 01:31:59.224
...reminds me of a
moment of foolishness...

01:32:00.833 --> 01:32:01.833
...from my past.

01:32:06.616 --> 01:32:10.325
An act I deeply regret.

01:32:11.641 --> 01:32:15.433
Something I did to
Dania and her mother.

01:32:17.199 --> 01:32:19.033
I took them for granted.

01:32:19.865 --> 01:32:20.865
Please...

01:32:23.399 --> 01:32:27.107
...don't ever do the same
thing to my daughter.

01:32:32.216 --> 01:32:33.109
Fais...

01:32:37.591 --> 01:32:39.008
...remember my words.

01:32:48.108 --> 01:32:49.775
If you're not able to do it...

01:32:51.631 --> 01:32:56.465
...the door to my home is still open
for you to return Dania to me.

01:33:00.707 --> 01:33:03.124
I'm begging for your
prayer and your blessing...

01:33:05.591 --> 01:33:07.442
...to go through with this.

01:33:09.716 --> 01:33:12.109
Because I know this is not easy.

01:33:14.250 --> 01:33:15.791
I ask for your prayer.

01:33:18.458 --> 01:33:20.208
I ask for your prayer.

01:33:21.250 --> 01:33:22.250
If God's willing...

01:33:23.791 --> 01:33:24.791
If God's willing...

01:33:27.583 --> 01:33:29.000
...I give you my blessing.

01:33:30.041 --> 01:33:31.294
I give you my blessing.

01:33:35.833 --> 01:33:36.916
I always pray...

01:33:39.216 --> 01:33:42.758
...for the good in your life. Okay?

01:33:50.541 --> 01:33:52.916
Maybe this is the last blessing I need.

01:34:01.090 --> 01:34:04.375
Allow me to be your husband's wife.

01:34:15.557 --> 01:34:17.253
In the name of God.

01:34:17.432 --> 01:34:21.812
I marry and give you in marriage,
Fais Hanip son of Abdullah...

01:34:22.183 --> 01:34:26.183
...to my daughter,
Bella Anindhiya daughter of Usman...

01:34:26.208 --> 01:34:29.166
...with a dowry of a complete set
of prayer equipment, paid in cash.

01:34:29.291 --> 01:34:31.875
I accept the marriage of Bella
Anindhiya daughter of Usman...

01:34:31.900 --> 01:34:33.983
...with the stated dowry, paid in cash.

01:34:34.491 --> 01:34:36.366
- Is it valid?
- It is!

01:34:36.500 --> 01:34:38.375
- Valid? Is it valid, everyone?
- It is!

01:34:38.458 --> 01:34:39.750
Thank God.

01:34:42.717 --> 01:34:43.892
Thank God.

01:34:57.458 --> 01:35:03.958
We now invite the bride
to enter the wedding hall.

01:37:12.416 --> 01:37:17.583
ONE YEAR LATER

01:37:27.291 --> 01:37:28.291
Be patient, Bella.

01:37:35.074 --> 01:37:36.483
Say God's name.

01:37:42.440 --> 01:37:43.815
Prepare the operation room.

01:37:44.415 --> 01:37:44.937
Yes, Doc.

01:37:45.030 --> 01:37:47.805
Mr. Fais, can I talk to
you outside for a moment?

01:37:54.499 --> 01:37:55.499
Bella.

01:37:56.241 --> 01:37:57.699
Keep saying God's name.

01:37:59.532 --> 01:38:01.198
Part of the placenta has detached.

01:38:01.949 --> 01:38:03.699
We need to act immediately.

01:38:04.500 --> 01:38:06.166
Oh, God.

01:38:09.666 --> 01:38:11.541
Excuse me, Doc.
Here's the letter of declaration.

01:38:11.890 --> 01:38:13.099
Sign this, please.

01:38:43.928 --> 01:38:46.261
Say God's name.

01:39:04.799 --> 01:39:07.716
This is exactly like when
you gave birth to Arumi.

01:39:19.458 --> 01:39:20.541
But why...

01:39:26.799 --> 01:39:28.317
Why am I more scared now?

01:39:35.848 --> 01:39:37.473
Let's keep praying, honey.

01:39:39.507 --> 01:39:43.507
May Bella and the baby be safe.

01:40:20.966 --> 01:40:21.966
How is it, Doc?

01:40:22.432 --> 01:40:24.816
Congrats, Mr. Fais and Mrs. Dania.

01:40:25.308 --> 01:40:26.558
Your baby was born in good health.

01:40:28.208 --> 01:40:29.666
Thank God.

01:40:31.132 --> 01:40:32.382
It's a boy.

01:40:37.165 --> 01:40:39.374
How's the mother?

01:40:42.732 --> 01:40:45.315
<i>After saving the baby...</i>

01:40:46.023 --> 01:40:47.773
<i>...there was severe bleeding.</i>

01:40:49.442 --> 01:40:53.400
<i>We tried our best to stop the bleeding.</i>

01:40:55.092 --> 01:40:57.925
<i>It was due to a fibroid...</i>

01:40:58.659 --> 01:41:00.608
<i>...which we have just discovered.</i>

01:41:01.560 --> 01:41:03.935
<i>Our efforts were unsuccessful.</i>

01:41:04.115 --> 01:41:06.865
<i>Bella's life couldn't be saved.</i>

01:41:08.849 --> 01:41:12.858
<i>She had the chance to</i>
<i>see and feel her baby...</i>

01:41:13.083 --> 01:41:15.833
<i>...before she breathed her last.</i>

01:41:30.357 --> 01:41:33.316
There is no god but Allah...

01:41:39.083 --> 01:41:42.083
...and Muhammad is the messenger of Allah.

01:42:06.000 --> 01:42:07.041
Oh, God.

01:42:11.151 --> 01:42:12.666
Oh, God.

01:42:39.849 --> 01:42:40.849
<i>I realize...</i>

01:42:42.739 --> 01:42:46.000
<i>...I'm merely a human</i>
<i>that needs a purpose in life.</i>

01:42:48.083 --> 01:42:51.666
<i>A purpose where I desire</i>
<i>worldly happiness...</i>

01:42:52.916 --> 01:42:56.500
<i>...and earn my place in heaven.</i>

01:43:19.715 --> 01:43:26.507
A FICTION THAT INSPIRED BY A TRUE EVENT

01:43:34.184 --> 01:43:35.019
<i>Bella...</i>

01:43:35.352 --> 01:43:38.398
<i>...look how handsome your baby son is.</i>

01:43:39.000 --> 01:43:42.416
<i>I will raise him with</i>
<i>the love you gave us.</i>

01:43:43.559 --> 01:43:46.392
<i>And I will tell him about you.</i>

01:43:47.733 --> 01:43:51.400
<i>He will know how</i>
<i>amazing his mother was.</i>